@* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
   FILTER + ALL MOVIES
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• *@
<div class="container" id="filter-section-container" style="margin-bottom:var(--sp-10)">
    <div class="sec-head">
        <div class="sec-head-left">
            <i class="fas fa-film" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <h2>Khám phá tất cả phim</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="sec-head-right">
            <button id="btnToggleFilter" class="filter-toggle-btn"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="filterBarPanel">
                <i class="fas fa-sliders-h" aria-hidden="true"></i> Bộ lọc
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="filter-panel" id="filterBarPanel" style="display:none" aria-hidden="true">
        <form method="get" asp-action="Index" asp-controller="Home" id="filterForm">
            <div class="filter-row">
                <div class="filter-group" style="flex:2; min-width:200px;">
                    <label for="cf-search"><i class="fas fa-search" aria-hidden="true"></i> Tìm kiếm</label>
                    <div class="search-wrap">
                        <input type="text" id="cf-search" name="search"
                               value="@f.Search"
                               placeholder="Tên phim..."
                               autocomplete="off" />
                        <button type="submit" aria-label="Tìm kiếm">
                            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="filter-group">
                    <label for="cf-genre"><i class="fas fa-theater-masks" aria-hidden="true"></i> Thể loại</label>
                    <select id="cf-genre" name="genreId" class="filter-select">
                        <option value="">Tất cả</option>
                        @foreach (var g in f.Genres)
                        {
                            <option value="@g.Id" selected="@(f.GenreId == g.Id ? "selected" : null)">@g.Name</option>
                        }
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="filter-group">
                    <label for="cf-country"><i class="fas fa-globe" aria-hidden="true"></i> Quốc gia</label>
                    <select id="cf-country" name="countryId" class="filter-select">
                        <option value="">Tất cả</option>
                        @foreach (var c in f.Countries)
                        {
                            <option value="@c.Id" selected="@(f.CountryId == c.Id ? "selected" : null)">@c.Name</option>
                        }
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="filter-group">
                    <label for="cf-type"><i class="fas fa-tv" aria-hidden="true"></i> Loại phim</label>
                    <select id="cf-type" name="type" class="filter-select">
                        <option value="">Tất cả</option>
                        <option value="1" selected="@(f.Type == 1 ? "selected" : null)">Movie</option>
                        <option value="2" selected="@(f.Type == 2 ? "selected" : null)">Series</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="filter-group">
                    <label for="cf-sort"><i class="fas fa-sort" aria-hidden="true"></i> Sắp xếp</label>
                    <select id="cf-sort" name="sortBy" class="filter-select">
                        <option value="latest" selected="@(f.SortBy == "latest" ? "selected" : null)">Mới nhất</option>
                        <option value="popular" selected="@(f.SortBy == "popular" ? "selected" : null)">Xem nhiều nhất</option>
                        <option value="title" selected="@(f.SortBy == "title" ? "selected" : null)">Tên A-Z</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="filter-group" style="justify-content:flex-end; flex-direction:row; align-items:flex-end;">
                    <a asp-action="Index" asp-controller="Home"
                       class="btn-reset-filter"
                       aria-label="Xóa tất cả bộ lọc">
                        <i class="fas fa-times"></i> Xóa lọc
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="filter-count" id="filter-count-wrapper">
                Đang hiển thị <strong>@f.Movies.Count</strong> / <strong>@f.TotalItems</strong> phim
                @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(f.Search) || f.GenreId.HasValue || f.CountryId.HasValue || f.Type.HasValue)
                {
                    <span style="color:var(--cf-text-lo)"> - đã lọc</span>
                }
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div id="filtered-movies-wrapper">
        @if (f.Movies.Any())
        {
            <div class="movies-grid">
                @foreach (var movie in f.Movies)
                {
                    <div class="grid-card">
                        <div class="grid-poster">
                            <span class="badge-type-card">@(movie.Type.ToString() == "Series" ? "Series" : "Movie")</span>
                            @if (movie.IsVipOnly)
                            {
                                <div class="badge-vip-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-crown"></i> VIP</div>
                            }
                            <a asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Detail" asp-route-slug="@movie.Slug"
                               aria-label="Xem chi tiết: @movie.Title">
                                <img src="@(string.IsNullOrEmpty(movie.PosterUrl) ? "https://via.placeholder.com/300x450/1c1c1c/555?text=No+Poster" : movie.PosterUrl)"
                                     alt="@movie.Title" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="300" height="450" />
                            </a>
                            <div class="grid-overlay">
                                <a asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Watch"
                                   asp-route-slug="@movie.Slug"
                                   class="btn-play-card"
                                   aria-label="Xem ngay: @movie.Title">
                                    <i class="fas fa-play" aria-hidden="true"></i> Xem ngay
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="grid-info">
                            <div class="grid-title">
                                <a asp-controller="Movie" asp-action="Detail" asp-route-slug="@movie.Slug">@movie.Title</a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="grid-meta">
                                @if (movie.ReleaseYear.HasValue)
                                {
                                    <span><i class="fas fa-calendar" aria-hidden="true"></i> @movie.ReleaseYear</span>
                                }
                                @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(movie.CountryName))
                                {
                                    <span>@movie.CountryName</span>
                                }
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                }
            </div>

            @if (f.TotalPages > 1)
            {
                int maxP = 5;
                int sP = Math.Max(1, f.PageNumber - maxP / 2);
                int eP = Math.Min(f.TotalPages, sP + maxP - 1);
                if (eP - sP + 1 < maxP) sP = Math.Max(1, eP - maxP + 1);

                <div class="pagination" role="navigation" aria-label="Phân trang">
                    <a asp-action="Index" asp-controller="Home"
                       asp-route-search="@f.Search" asp-route-genreId="@f.GenreId"
                       asp-route-countryId="@f.CountryId" asp-route-type="@f.Type"
                       asp-route-sortBy="@f.SortBy" asp-route-pageNumber="@(f.PageNumber - 1)"
                       class="page-btn @(!f.HasPreviousPage ? "disabled" : null)"
                       aria-label="Trang trước">
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i>
                    </a>
                    @for (int pi = sP; pi <= eP; pi++)
                    {
                        <a asp-action="Index" asp-controller="Home"
                           asp-route-search="@f.Search" asp-route-genreId="@f.GenreId"
                           asp-route-countryId="@f.CountryId" asp-route-type="@f.Type"
                           asp-route-sortBy="@f.SortBy" asp-route-pageNumber="@pi"
                           class="page-btn @(pi == f.PageNumber ? "active" : null)"
                           aria-current="@(pi == f.PageNumber ? "page" : null)"
                           aria-label="Trang @pi">@pi</a>
                    }
                    <a asp-action="Index" asp-controller="Home"
                       asp-route-search="@f.Search" asp-route-genreId="@f.GenreId"
                       asp-route-countryId="@f.CountryId" asp-route-type="@f.Type"
                       asp-route-sortBy="@f.SortBy" asp-route-pageNumber="@(f.PageNumber + 1)"
                       class="page-btn @(!f.HasNextPage ? "disabled" : null)"
                       aria-label="Trang sau">
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            }
        }
        else
        {
            <div class="empty-state">
                <i class="fas fa-search" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                <h3>Không tìm thấy phim phù hợp</h3>
                <p>Thử điều chỉnh bộ lọc, hoặc <a asp-action="Index" asp-controller="Home">xóa tất cả bộ lọc</a>.</p>
            </div>
        }
    </div>
</div>

@Html.AntiForgeryToken()

@section Scripts {
    <script>
        /* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
           HERO SLIDER
        â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
        (function(){
            const slides     = document.querySelectorAll('.hero-slide');
            const thumbs     = document.querySelectorAll('.thumb-item');
            const dots       = document.querySelectorAll('.cf-dot');
            const total      = slides.length;
            if (!total) return;

            let current = 0;
            let timer;

            function goto(idx) {
                slides[current].classList.remove('active');
                thumbs[current]?.classList.remove('active');
                dots[current]?.classList.remove('active');
                thumbs[current]?.setAttribute('aria-selected','false');
                dots[current]?.setAttribute('aria-selected','false');

                current = ((idx % total) + total) % total;

                slides[current].classList.add('active');
                thumbs[current]?.classList.add('active');
                dots[current]?.classList.add('active');
                thumbs[current]?.setAttribute('aria-selected','true');
                dots[current]?.setAttribute('aria-selected','true');

                // Auto-scroll thumbnail into view
                const strip = document.querySelector('.hero-thumbs');
                const th = thumbs[current];
                if (strip && th) {
                    const tl = th.offsetLeft, tw = th.offsetWidth, sw = strip.offsetWidth;
                    if (tl < strip.scrollLeft || tl + tw > strip.scrollLeft + sw) {
                        strip.scrollTo({ left: tl - sw/2 + tw/2, behavior:'smooth' });
                    }
                }
            }

            function next() { goto(current + 1); }
            function reset() { clearInterval(timer); if (total > 1) timer = setInterval(next, 8000); }

            thumbs.forEach(t => t.addEventListener('click', () => { goto(+t.dataset.slide); reset(); }));
            dots.forEach(d => d.addEventListener('click', () => { goto(+d.dataset.slide); reset(); }));

            document.addEventListener('keydown', e => {
                if (e.key === 'ArrowLeft')  { goto(current - 1); reset(); }
                if (e.key === 'ArrowRight') { next(); reset(); }
            });

            reset();
        })();

        /* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
           ROW SCROLL HELPERS
        â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
        function cfScroll(id, dir) {
            const el = document.getElementById(id + '-movies-row');
            if (el) el.scrollBy({ left: dir * 640, behavior: 'smooth' });
        }

        /* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
           FILTER TOGGLE
        â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
        (function(){
            const btn   = document.getElementById('btnToggleFilter');
            const panel = document.getElementById('filterBarPanel');
            if (!btn || !panel) return;

            // Auto-open if filters are active
            if (window.location.search.length > 1) {
                panel.style.display = 'block';
                panel.setAttribute('aria-hidden','false');
                btn.classList.add('active');
                btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded','true');
            }

            btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
                const open = panel.style.display !== 'none';
                panel.style.display = open ? 'none' : 'block';
                panel.setAttribute('aria-hidden', open ? 'true' : 'false');
                btn.classList.toggle('active', !open);
                btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', String(!open));
            });

            // Auto-submit on select change
            document.querySelectorAll('#filterForm select').forEach(sel => {
                sel.addEventListener('change', () => document.getElementById('filterForm').submit());
            });
        })();

        /* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
           AJAX FILTER + PAGINATION
        â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
        $(document).ready(function(){
            $(document).on('submit','#filterForm', function(e){
                e.preventDefault();
                loadFiltered($(this).attr('action') + '?' + $(this).serialize());
            });

            $(document).on('click','.pagination a.page-btn', function(e){
                e.preventDefault();
                const url = $(this).attr('href');
                if (url && !$(this).hasClass('disabled')) {
                    loadFiltered(url);
                    $('html,body').animate({ scrollTop: $('#filter-section-container').offset().top - 60 }, 400);
                }
            });

            function loadFiltered(url) {
                const $w = $('#filtered-movies-wrapper');
                $w.css('opacity',.4);
                const separator = url.indexOf('?') !== -1 ? '&' : '?';
                const partialUrl = url + separator + 'partial=true';
                $.get(partialUrl, function(data){
                    const $d = $(data);
                    $('#filter-count-wrapper').html($d.find('#filter-count-wrapper').html());
                    $w.html($d.find('#filtered-movies-wrapper').html());
                    $w.css('opacity',1);
                    window.history.pushState({}, '', url);
                }).fail(function(){
                    $w.css('opacity',1);
                });
            }

            /* Search suggestions */
            let searchTimer;
            $(document).on('input','.searchInputField', function(){
                clearTimeout(searchTimer);
                const q = $(this).val().trim();
                const box = $(this).closest('.banner-search-container').find('.searchSuggestionsBox');
                if (q.length < 2) { box.hide(); return; }
                searchTimer = setTimeout(() => {
                    $.get('/Search/Suggestions', { q }, function(data){
                        box.empty();
                        if (data?.length) {
                            data.forEach(m => {
                                box.append(`<a href="/Movie/Detail/${m.slug}" class="suggestion-item">
                                    <img src="${m.posterUrl}" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/40x60/1c1c1c/555?text=N/A'" alt="${m.title}"/>
                                    <div>
                                        <div style="font-weight:700">${m.title}</div>
                                        <div style="font-size:.8rem;color:#888"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i> ${m.year||'N/A'}</div>
                                    </div>
                                </a>`);
                            });
                            box.fadeIn(150);
                        } else {
                            box.html('<div style="padding:14px;color:#888;text-align:center">Không tìm thấy kết quả</div>').fadeIn(150);
                        }
                    });
                }, 300);
            });

            $(document).on('click', function(e){
                if (!$(e.target).closest('.banner-search-container').length)
                    $('.searchSuggestionsBox').fadeOut(150);
            });
        });
    </script>
}



